; Back side outer profile cut (releases the part)
; Tool: 2mm single flute spiral end mill
; Material: 3/16" brass on fixture plate
; X0 Y0 = plate center (BACK SIDE - brass flipped left-right)
; Z0 = top of brass

G21       ; metric
G90       ; absolute
G17       ; XY plane for arcs
M3 S10000 ; spindle on
G4 P2     ; spin-up dwell

; Toolpath is the SVG outline OFFSET OUTWARD by 1.0mm
; so the finished part lands at the design dimensions.
; Total depth: 5.013mm (through brass + into fixture)
; The three tab pins keep the part registered after release.

